Package: simITS
Type: Package
Title: Analysis via Simulation of Interrupted Time Series (ITS) Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Luke Miratrix, Brit Henderson, Chloe Anderson
Maintainer: Luke Miratrix <lmiratrix@g.harvard.edu>
Description: Uses simulation to create prediction intervals for post-policy outcomes in Interrupted Time Series (ITS) designs.
    This work partially supported by the Arnold Foundation in collaboration with MDRC.
